ReviewText:
As a regular drinker of espresso coffee from my Nespresso machine I thought I would try this - after all Nescafe and Nespresso are both part of the Nestlé  group. It was a huge mistake; you may like this product as a drink in its own right (I don't) but it certainly is not espresso coffee as my palate understands it.

My recommendation - avoid at all costs.
